I would like to provide a transparant update: I am working with the reporters of #2012469 to define the boundaries of their report. A case COULD be made it's a duplicate but that is currently rather controversial. I have laid down a proposal for them and am awaiting their feedback, if they disagree with that feedback we will engage mediation for a final ruling. Dependent on if we consider that report a full duplicate of #2096271 or a partial duplicate of #2096271 defines whether or not this report is valid (full bounty) or duplicate (of #2012469). This process might take some time dependent on the outcome but I'd rather do things right than rush them and do it wrong :) I hope you understand.

